reviewText: exactly what i was waiting for
it was a very good movie. i've watched before but never finished it. so had to make sure I saw the end so I bought it.

I truly recommend Money or Bullets this indie film was at the Oaxaca Film Festival which I attended.
And I got to tell you Mr. Human I take my hats off to you!  I can't believe you were able to tell this
story with practically no budget!  It was an honor to meet you and I hope to see many more films
from you in the future.

I highly recommend you see this film!  Great Story! Very Original and Well shot!!!!
The story of a guy who's running away from a powerful drug dealer trying to keep from trouble gets caught up in the drug business.  I liked his words of  reflection at the end.
